SUMMARY:Motorcycle Riding Experience with Cascade Motorcycle Safety
DESCRIPTION:Want to ride a motorcycle but don’t know where to start? Join Cascade Motorcycle Safety and Ride With Us for a chance to experience riding a motorcycle for free\, with professional Cascade Motorcycle Safety RiderCoaches helping you through each step. These 1-on-1\, 20-minute sessions are designed for total beginners\, with bikes and helmets provided. \nThis program is presented with the support of Cascade Motorcycle Safety. \nRide out the remainder of the day in MOHAI to see Kickstands Up! 125 Years of Motorcycling in the PNW. Program participants will receive a coupon for $5 off museum admission. \nAs of 2/18/26\, the location and time of this event has changed.
URL:https://mohai.org/event/motorcycle-riding-experience-with-cascade-motorcycle-safety/
LOCATION:South Seattle College North Parking Lot\, 6000 16th Ave SW\, Seattle\, WA\, 98106\, United States
CATEGORIES:Hobbies,People & Culture,Sports
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://mohai.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/motorcycle-riding-lessons_Hero.jpg
END:VEVENT
