SUMMARY:Kickstands Up! All Motorcycle Club Day
DESCRIPTION:Inviting all motorcycle clubs to roll on down to MOHAI! Indicate your Motorcycle Cub membership and receive $5 off admission all day\, and explore Kickstands Up: 125 Years of Motorcycling in the Pacific Northwest with gallery talks by exhibit co-curators from the Pacific Northwest Museum of Motorcycling from 2-4pm. \nSpots are limited and are assigned on a first-come\, first-served basis. \nFor accessibility support\, please contact programs@mohai.org two weeks before the event.
